data.description: Your new home is waiting!! This adorable 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Ranch is well within a sought-after community in the Dutchtown School district. Upon entry, you'll be welcomed by a spacious open-concept floor plan. Step into the Cozy Family Room to find Soaring Vaulted Ceilings and a Fireplace. The Spacious Open Kitchen also Boasts Vaulted Ceilings, ample Cabinets, a Kitchen Island with a Breakfast Bar, and a Pantry. This home has a Large Master Suite w/Trey Ceiling and Walk-in Closet. The Front Hallway leads to Secondary Bedrooms with ample Space. The community features a resort-style Olympic Swimming Pool with a Waterslide and Fountain, 7 Tennis Courts, a Clubhouse, a Lake, Playground, and Several Walking Trails. The home has a supra lockbox for access.
